  "detailed_description": "<h1>Plays Great on Steam Deck</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700360/extras/f2800273c2ea9404921fb74b01ec2251.avif?t=1770928824\" width=551 height=179 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700360/extras/7a63f491def700b1e846c8f59e5ed38f.avif?t=1770928824\" width=570 height=102 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Local party brawler for 1–4 players</strong> (solo or couch co-op)<br><i>Online via Steam Remote Play Together</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Battle, Story, and Arcade modes</strong><br>Campaign through handcrafted levels or jump into quick matches</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build and destroy castles</strong> during combat using traps and defenses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Melee and ranged combat</strong> that’s easy to learn, hard to master</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>4 battlegrounds</strong> with distinct layouts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>16 buildable weapons and defenses</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700360/extras/b03fe204bcd47c5f3ef68609ce10bd0c.avif?t=1770928824\" width=620 height=247 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Battle</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each match begins with both teams building a castle equipped with cannons. Once the fight starts, destroy the opposing base and knock out the king or queen to win the round. The first team to score <strong>three K.O.s</strong> wins the match. After each round, you can rebuild and adjust your castle.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Story</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play through a short campaign across multiple levels, solo or in local co-op. Defeat enemies, expand your arsenal, and unlock new kingdoms as you progress. The story is light-hearted and supported by short cinematic cutscenes.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Arcade</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defend your castle against waves of enemies, solo or in local co-op. Enemies drop gold, which can be used to upgrade your castle between waves. Track your performance on online leaderboards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700360/extras/34d42ece40bc08a35552d30bf3cb493c.avif?t=1770928824\" width=570 height=139 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700360/extras/c3561961bfa0d8738bff4970df86e57d.poster.avif?t=1770928824\" width=620 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700360/extras/c3561961bfa0d8738bff4970df86e57d.webm?t=1770928824\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700360/extras/c3561961bfa0d8738bff4970df86e57d.mp4?t=1770928824\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700360/extras/7a63f491def700b1e846c8f59e5ed38f.avif?t=1770928824\" width=570 height=102 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Local party brawler for 1–4 players</strong> (solo or couch co-op)<br><i>Online via Steam Remote Play Together</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Battle, Story, and Arcade modes</strong><br>Campaign through handcrafted levels or jump into quick matches</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build and destroy castles</strong> during combat using traps and defenses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Melee and ranged combat</strong> that’s easy to learn, hard to master</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>4 battlegrounds</strong> with distinct layouts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>16 buildable weapons and defenses</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700360/extras/b03fe204bcd47c5f3ef68609ce10bd0c.avif?t=1770928824\" width=620 height=247 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Battle</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each match begins with both teams building a castle equipped with cannons. Once the fight starts, destroy the opposing base and knock out the king or queen to win the round. The first team to score <strong>three K.O.s</strong> wins the match. After each round, you can rebuild and adjust your castle.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Story</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play through a short campaign across multiple levels, solo or in local co-op. Defeat enemies, expand your arsenal, and unlock new kingdoms as you progress. The story is light-hearted and supported by short cinematic cutscenes.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Arcade</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defend your castle against waves of enemies, solo or in local co-op. Enemies drop gold, which can be used to upgrade your castle between waves. Track your performance on online leaderboards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700360/extras/34d42ece40bc08a35552d30bf3cb493c.avif?t=1770928824\" width=570 height=139 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700360/extras/c3561961bfa0d8738bff4970df86e57d.poster.avif?t=1770928824\" width=620 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700360/extras/c3561961bfa0d8738bff4970df86e57d.webm?t=1770928824\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700360/extras/c3561961bfa0d8738bff4970df86e57d.mp4?t=1770928824\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
